snippet.title: Liminal Exploration
snippet.description:
Made for the #cursedimagejam
Albeit somewhat wacky game, yet alas, a cursed liminal game it is!
https://tmdev.itch.io/liminalexplorer
This gameplay trailer here features Red Sprites by @CicadaSirens who also did the full soundtrack.
#indiedev #gamedev #lowpoly #PS1
